    "title": "Gathering Training Videos for an Action Classifier"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Create a robust action classifier by collecting high-quality videos that clearly",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "show a person performing each action you want the classifier to recognize. In addition,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "gather videos of unrelated actions the classifier might witness. Use these to create",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "negative class",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " of irrelevant actions, so the classifier distinguishes between",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "these two types.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For general information about how to create an action classifier, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.CreateML/documentation/CreateML/creating-an-action-classifier-model",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Collect-Videos-for-Each-Action",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Collect Videos for Each Action",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Action classifiers learn from example videos of a human performing an action. Create",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "ML uses the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Vision",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " framework to locate",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "key body parts, called ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "landmarks",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": ", in each video frame. Action classifiers learn",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "how to recognize a human body’s movements by tracking these landmarks frame by frame.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Keep the landmarks clearly visible by applying the following guidelines as you record",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "example videos, or when assessing videos from other sources.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Keep the camera still.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Record one person at a time.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Capture the person’s entire body.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ensure the environment has sufficient lighting.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ensure the person’s clothing isn’t loose or flowing.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ensure the person’s clothing sufficiently contrasts with the environment’s background.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Remove foreground objects that might obscure the person as they perform the action.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "If the person performs multiple instances of a single action in a recording, minimize",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "the time between repetitions.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You typically want an action classifier to work with any human that uses your app.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Teach your model to account for natural variations by including videos of variations",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in the action you want the classifier to recognize, such as how the person holds",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "their head or places their arms.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you want your app to recognize actions more generally or from various camera angles,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "add more example videos that capture the action from multiple directions.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Collect-Videos-for-a-Negative-Class",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Collect Videos for a Negative Class",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A negative class is a category of one or more actions that aren’t important to the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "action classifier. Negative classes help the classifier distinguish between the actions",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you want it to recognize and potential nonactions it might encounter in your app.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Create a negative class by gathering example videos of all unrelated nonactions the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "classifier might observe. For example, a negative class for an exercise-action classifier",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "might include examples of individuals walking in and out frame. Including this negative",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "class ensures that the action classifier is less likely to confuse walking for an",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "exercise, such as a lunge.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Make additional negative classes for nonactions that take different spans of time,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or for static versus dynamic nonactions. For example, the exercise classifier might",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "have another negative class of static actions that include examples of individuals",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "standing still or sitting in a chair.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
